    <div class="sc pageBody">
        <div id="container">
            




<div class="content_container news_content">

    <div class="columns cols col-106">

        <div class="col col1">
            

            <div class="article">

                



<div class="marketName">
   <div class="marketNamePadding">
      <div class="marketNameContainer">
         <div class="marketNameWrapper">
            <h1>买方和卖方对市场价格的影响</h1>
         </div>
      </div>
   </div>
</div>

                <div class="intro text_ig parbase">








   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
      
   

</div>

                <div class="share-top social-sharing parbase">








    <div class="sharebanner  ">
        <ul>
            
                <li class="share-label">
                    share
                </li>
            
            
                
                    
                        <li><a id="share-weibu" class="group openPopup share-link share-link-old share-weibu" href="http://service.weibo.com/share/share.php?url=https://www.ig.com/zh/trading-ideas/buyer-seller-impact-on-price-40457-171031&appkey=&title=%E4%B9%B0%E6%96%B9%E5%92%8C%E5%8D%96%E6%96%B9%E5%AF%B9%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E4%BB%B7%E6%A0%BC%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D&pic=&ralateUid=&language=zh_cn" target="_blank" title="Weibo">
                        </a></li>
                    
                    
                
                
            
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

                <div class="author news-article-author parbase"><a class="author-profile" href="/zh/profile/ig-simplified"><img class="author-image" src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/dam/publicsites/1422061621672/aum/images/Other/lp_IG_logo.jpg" alt="IG集团"></a>
        <div class="news-article-author-details">
            <p class="news-article-author-name">
                <a href="/zh/profile/ig-simplified">IG集团</a><br />
                        Market Analyst</p>
            <p class="news-article-timestamp time" data-datetime="2017-10-31T05:37:41+0000">2017-10-31T05:37:41+0000</p>
        </div>
    </div>

                








                <div class="article_intro">
                    <div class="newspar2 parsys">
</div>

                    <div class="textimage parbase">





<div class="text"><p>交易者是金融市场的参与者，无论是基于什么原因和目的参与到市场中，即使我们也常常将交易者划分为：对冲避险者、投机获利者、长期价值投资者、高频交易者等多种类型，但只要参与到金融市场中，就必须成为买方或者卖方之一。因此，所有参与者最终都可以划分为买方或者卖方。这种划分方式极大简化了交易者对市场的分析工作。</p>

<p>买方，通常称之为多头；是价格上涨，市场走牛的基本推动力量；当买方逐步增多，力量逐步增强时，代表价格会上涨。卖方，通常称之为空头，是价格下跌，市场走熊的基本推动力量；当卖方逐步增多，力量逐步增强时，代表价格会下跌。因此，每一位交易者的进场方向对整体市场的走势有一定的影响，只是由于单个交易者或者单个交易机构对金融市场的影响太小，小到不足以影响市场价格的波动，因此常常会被市场忽略，但任何人都无法怀疑这种影响的存在。特殊的情况也会经常发生，比如央行对外汇市场的干预，当数百亿甚至数千亿美元同时进入市场而干预汇率走势时，我们会看到这种单一力量对汇率价格的明显影响。</p>

<p>有时候，买方和卖方的界限并不那么清晰，在同一笔交易中，一个交易者可以既是买方又是卖方。当买方进场后，实际上已经成为了一名潜在的卖方，因为买方可能随时平仓出场，将原本多单平仓时，相当于在市场上成交了相同数量的空单。作为买方，当他进场时是买方，但出场时就成了卖方。如果交易者看涨行情，他会先买后卖；如果交易者看空行情，他会先卖后买。一买一卖是每一笔交易必须进行的操作，只不过时间和价位不同而已。</p>
</div><div class="clear"></div></div>

                </div>
                <div class="newspar3 parsys"><div class="new-content-component section">


















<div class="content content-component">
    <div
    
            
            
            class="theme
            
            none-bg dark-text-theme
            image-layout-full-bottom
            
            
            
            text-position-top
            
            imagesize50
            
            
            js_clickable 
            
            
            
            ">

        
            <div class="image text-image">
                









    
    <span data-link="" data-classnames="" data-alt="" class="lazyload adaptive-image">
        
        
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/trading-ideas/2017/10/31/buyer-seller-impact-on-price-40457/_jcr_content/newspar3/content_component.adaptive.320.medium.png/1509428077701.png"  data-width="952" data-height="698" data-media="(min-width: 1px)"></span>
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/trading-ideas/2017/10/31/buyer-seller-impact-on-price-40457/_jcr_content/newspar3/content_component.adaptive.320.high.png/1509428077701.png"    data-width="952" data-height="698" data-media="(min-width: 320px)"></span>  
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/trading-ideas/2017/10/31/buyer-seller-impact-on-price-40457/_jcr_content/newspar3/content_component.adaptive.480.high.png/1509428077701.png"    data-width="952" data-height="698" data-media="(min-width: 321px)"></span>  
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/trading-ideas/2017/10/31/buyer-seller-impact-on-price-40457/_jcr_content/newspar3/content_component.adaptive.476.high.png/1509428077701.png"    data-width="952" data-height="698" data-media="(min-width: 481px)"></span>   
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/trading-ideas/2017/10/31/buyer-seller-impact-on-price-40457/_jcr_content/newspar3/content_component.adaptive.620.high.png/1509428077701.png"    data-width="952" data-height="698" data-media="(min-width: 769px)"></span>  
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/trading-ideas/2017/10/31/buyer-seller-impact-on-price-40457/_jcr_content/newspar3/content_component.adaptive.full.high.png/1509428077701.png"   data-width="952" data-height="698" data-media="(min-width: 1025px)"></span> 
        
            
           <noscript>
               
                   <img src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/trading-ideas/2017/10/31/buyer-seller-impact-on-price-40457/_jcr_content/newspar3/content_component.adaptive.320.low.png/1509428077701.png" alt="">
                   
           </noscript>
    </span>

            </div><div class="clearfix"></div>

        
        
    </div>
</div></div>
<div class="new-content-component section">


















<div class="content content-component">
    <div
    
            
            
            class="theme
            
            none-bg dark-text-theme
            image-layout-full-bottom
            
            
            
            text-position-top
            text-no-image
            imagesize50
            
            
            js_clickable 
            
            
            
            ">

        <div class="text text-content"
                     >
                






    
    
        
    



                





        <p>对于交易者而言，如果进场的方向是做空，那么就属于卖方，当市场价格下跌时，交易者就会处于收益状态；反之，在交易者进场后，市场价格上涨，那么该交易者就处于亏损的状态；因此做空的交易者，希望价格下跌。而在市场的另一面，如果交易者进场的方向是买入，称之为多头，只有当价格上涨时才会处于收益状态，价格下跌时就处于亏损状态了。</p>


                
            </div><div class="clearfix"></div>

        
        
    </div>
</div></div>
<div class="new-content-component section">


















<div class="content content-component">
    <div
    
            
            
            class="theme
            
            none-bg dark-text-theme
            image-layout-full-bottom
            
            
            
            text-position-top
            
            imagesize50
            
            
            js_clickable 
            
            
            
            ">

        
            <div class="image text-image">
                









    
    <span data-link="" data-classnames="" data-alt="" class="lazyload adaptive-image">
        
        
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/trading-ideas/2017/10/31/buyer-seller-impact-on-price-40457/_jcr_content/newspar3/content_component_2083855503.adaptive.320.medium.png/1509428151900.png"  data-width="1280" data-height="467" data-media="(min-width: 1px)"></span>
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/trading-ideas/2017/10/31/buyer-seller-impact-on-price-40457/_jcr_content/newspar3/content_component_2083855503.adaptive.320.high.png/1509428151900.png"    data-width="1280" data-height="467" data-media="(min-width: 320px)"></span>  
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/trading-ideas/2017/10/31/buyer-seller-impact-on-price-40457/_jcr_content/newspar3/content_component_2083855503.adaptive.480.high.png/1509428151900.png"    data-width="1280" data-height="467" data-media="(min-width: 321px)"></span>  
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/trading-ideas/2017/10/31/buyer-seller-impact-on-price-40457/_jcr_content/newspar3/content_component_2083855503.adaptive.476.high.png/1509428151900.png"    data-width="1280" data-height="467" data-media="(min-width: 481px)"></span>   
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/trading-ideas/2017/10/31/buyer-seller-impact-on-price-40457/_jcr_content/newspar3/content_component_2083855503.adaptive.620.high.png/1509428151900.png"    data-width="1280" data-height="467" data-media="(min-width: 769px)"></span>  
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/trading-ideas/2017/10/31/buyer-seller-impact-on-price-40457/_jcr_content/newspar3/content_component_2083855503.adaptive.full.high.png/1509428151900.png"   data-width="1280" data-height="467" data-media="(min-width: 1025px)"></span> 
        
            
           <noscript>
               
                   <img src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/trading-ideas/2017/10/31/buyer-seller-impact-on-price-40457/_jcr_content/newspar3/content_component_2083855503.adaptive.320.low.png/1509428151900.png" alt="">
                   
           </noscript>
    </span>

            </div><div class="clearfix"></div>

        
        
    </div>
</div></div>
<div class="new-content-component section">


















<div class="content content-component">
    <div
    
            
            
            class="theme
            
            none-bg dark-text-theme
            image-layout-full-bottom
            
            
            
            text-position-top
            text-no-image
            imagesize50
            
            
            js_clickable 
            
            
            
            ">

        <div class="text text-content"
                     >
                






    
    
        
    



                





        <p>无论价格是上涨还是下跌，总有人收益或者亏损，市场的涨跌不是决定交易者盈利或者亏损的关键，重要的是交易者所处的方向是否与市场走势一致。</p>

<p>因此，在交易外汇或者<a href="https://www.ig.com/zh/cfd-trading">差价合约</a>时，如何正确判断市场的方向并提前进场成了交易者关注的焦点。特别是在差价合约交易中，由于交易者不持有真实的资产，纯粹的关注价格涨跌方向和空间距离成了交易者的重点。</p>


                
            </div><div class="clearfix"></div>

        
        
    </div>
</div></div>

</div>

